# =============================================================================
# x3miptv.cfg.example
# =============================================================================
# Copy this file to x3miptv.cfg and edit it with your provider details.
# x3miptv.cfg is gitignored to protect your credentials.
#
# FORMAT
# ------
# Each non-blank, non-comment line defines one IPTV provider source.
# Fields are pipe-separated (|).
#
# M3U provider (direct playlist URL):
#   M3U|<full_url>
#
#   The URL can be HTTP or HTTPS. Examples:
#     M3U|http://provider.com/playlist.m3u
#     M3U|https://provider.com/playlist.m3u8
#     M3U|https://provider.com:8443/get.php?username=user&password=pass&type=m3u_plus
#
# Xtream Codes provider (server + credentials):
#   XC|<server_url>|<username>|<password>
#
#   The script constructs the M3U URL from your credentials automatically.
#   Include the protocol (http/https) and port in the server URL. Examples:
#     XC|http://provider.com:8080|myuser|mypassword
#     XC|https://provider.com:8443|myuser|mypassword
#     XC|https://provider.com|myuser|mypassword
#
# Lines beginning with # are treated as comments and ignored.
# Blank lines are ignored.
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# FREE PUBLIC EXAMPLE - iptv-org UK channels
# A community-maintained, legitimately free playlist. Safe to leave in place
# for testing. See https://github.com/iptv-org/iptv for other regions/categories.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
M3U|https://iptv-org.github.io/iptv/countries/gb.m3u

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# YOUR PROVIDERS - uncomment and edit as needed
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Example M3U provider
# M3U|https://yourprovider.com/get.php?username=user&password=pass&type=m3u_plus&output=mpegts

# Example Xtream Codes provider (HTTP)
# XC|http://yourprovider.com:8080|yourusername|yourpassword

# Example Xtream Codes provider (HTTPS)
# XC|https://yourprovider.com:8443|yourusername|yourpassword

# You can add as many providers as you like - all domains and IPs are
# accumulated and deduplicated before updating x3mRouting.
